# Privacy Policy for "DISHA Computer"

Effective Date: 14 Feb, 2026
Application Name: DISHA Computer

---

## Introduction

DISHA Computer is an Android application developed for students of "Disha Computer Education Haladi". The app provides access to educational content such as courses, quizzes, DISHA AI.

We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and how we protect it in accordance with Google Play policies and applicable data protection laws.

By using this application, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

---

## Data Collection

DISHA Computer may collect the following information:

### 1. Personal Information (Provided by User)

* Full Name
* Email Address
* Password (stored securely in encrypted form)

This information is required to create and manage your student account.

### 2. Educational Information

* Course enrollments
* Quiz answers and results
* Learning progress

### 3. Technical Information

* Device information (Android version, device type)
* App usage logs

---

## Data Usage

The collected data is used only for educational and operational purposes, including:

* Account creation and login authentication
* Providing access to courses and learning materials
* Managing quizzes and displaying results
* Sending important notifications
* Improving app performance and stability

We do NOT:

* Sell user data
* Share personal data for advertising
* Use data for marketing profiling
* Collect unnecessary sensitive information

---

## Data Sharing

We do not sell or rent your personal information.

Your data may only be accessed by authorized administrators or teachers of "Disha Computer Education Haladi" for academic management purposes.

Data may be disclosed only if required by law.

---

## User Rights

Users have the right to:

* Access their account information
* Update or correct personal details
* Request account deletion

To request deletion or corrections, please contact us using the email below.

---

## Data Retention

We retain user data only:

* While the student account remains active
* As required for academic records
* As required by applicable laws

Upon request, user accounts and associated data can be deleted.

---

## Security Measures

We implement appropriate security practices to protect user information, including:

* Encrypted password storage
* Secure backend APIs
* Restricted access to administrative data
* Protection against unauthorized access

While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your information, no system can guarantee absolute security.

---

## Permissions Used

DISHA Computer may request:

* Internet Permission – to access courses, and quizzes
* Notification Permission – to send academic updates and announcements
* Camera - to watch your moments on final exam only

The app does NOT access:

* Contacts
* Location
* Microphone

unless explicitly introduced in future updates.

---

## Children’s Privacy

This app is intended for enrolled students of Disha Computer Education Haladi. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13 without appropriate consent.

---

## Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy if the app functionality changes. Any modifications will be reflected by updating this page and revising the Effective Date.

We encourage users to review this policy periodically.

---

## Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: dishacomputerhaladi@gmail.com
Developer: DISHA Computer Education Haladi
